[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]4.7. 
[normal]The need for support for rural services needs to be seen as a given; there are clearly exceptions that geograph
[normal]y etc. may help, but on the whole there is little scope for making rural services sustainable. 
[normal]Kick-starting CT schemes with short-term funding is unlikely to make new services financially sustainable long
[normal]-
[normal]term 
[normal]as the 
[normal]shortfall between cost and revenue wil
[normal]l continue. 
